data.description: Check out this 3 bed/2 bath Solar home in Desert Sky! This adorable home was built in 2020 and features soaring ceilings above the open-concept main space. Spacious eat-in kitchen boasts granite counters, dark cabinetry and a walk-in pantry. Three nice-sized bedrooms and two full baths make up the rest of the 2101 sq ft interior. Backyard is a blank canvas, ready for you to add your own personal touch. Great location near shopping and restaurants.
